stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_load: load blobSchedule from EL config
    q_load --> q_iter: for each fork in blobSchedule
    q_iter --> q_check_time: read fork activation timestamp
    q_check_time --> q_match: current_time >= fork activation timestamp
    q_check_time --> q_iter: current_time < fork activation timestamp
    q_match --> q_resolve: resolve target, max, baseFeeUpdateFraction
    q_resolve --> q_iter: check next fork for later override
    q_iter --> q_validate: no more forks
    q_validate --> [*]: return resolved BlobSchedule(target, max, baseFeeUpdateFraction)
